+- `InternalEnergySolverConfig::under_relaxation`
+- `CopyCurrentOhmicSource()`
+- `ComputeConvergenceStats()`
+- `CheckThermalConvergence()`
+- `AcceptNextIterate()`
+- any outer loop of the form “repeat until converged or max_iter”
